revision.text:
The KEYCONF lump deals primarily with keybindings in a [[WAD]] file. It allows weapons to be added or removed from any game [[ZDoom]] supports ([[Doom]], [[Hexen]], [[Heretic]], and [[Strife]]), as well as binding additional commands for use in conjunction with a script.

* [[Adding weaponsections]] {{deprecated}}
* [[Adding keysections]]

KEYCONF is actually a limited [[Console Commands|console]] script that is automatically executed when the wad it appears in is loaded. It only accepts the following commands:

* {{CCMD|C|alias}}
* {{CCMD|C|defaultbind}}
* {{CCMD|C|addkeysection}}
* {{CCMD|C|addmenukey}}
* {{CCMD|C|addslotdefault}}
* {{CCMD|C|weaponsection}}
* {{CCMD|C|setslot}} {{deprecated}}
* {{CCMD|C|clearplayerclasses}} {{deprecated}}
* {{CCMD|C|addplayerclass}} {{deprecated}}
[[Category:ZDoom special lumps]]
